content.rendered:
Benefits Specialist | Tulsa, OK Benefits Specialist Preferences:
  • Licensed in life, accident and health
Benefits Specialist Requirements:
  • Ability to cold call businesses and set a meeting
  • Ability to sell insurance to both residential and business customers
Benefits Specialist Compensation:
  • 24k-30k base plus commission
